<i>noun</i>: 평일 [평일] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>평일 [평일]</dt><br>
<dd>1. ordinary times</dd><br>
<dd>특별한 일이 없는 보통 때.</dd><br>
<dd>Ordinary times in which nothing special is happening.</dd><br>
<dd>2. weekday</dd><br>
<dd>토요일, 일요일, 공휴일이 아닌 보통 날.</dd><br>
<dd>A day which is not Saturday, Sunday, or a holiday.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>